<h1><a href="http://thinkprogress.org/economy/2013/11/18/2960371/walmart-food-drive/">Walmart Holding Canned Food Drive For Its Own Underpaid Employees</a></h1>

<div class="post">

<p class="timestamp">
	<span class="byline"> by <a href="http://thinkprogress.org/?person=scott-keyes">Scott Keyes</a> </span><span class="posted-on">Posted on <time class="published" datetime="November 18, 2013 at 12:50 pm">November 18, 2013 at 12:50 pm</time>&nbsp;<time class="updated" datetime="November 18, 2013 at 1:04 pm">Updated: November 18, 2013 at 1:04 pm</time></span></p>


